          Join the leading apparel and footwear brands building their digital identity strategy on TieBack.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6" data-ps="src/pages/industries/textiles.astro:8ygl38">
          <button class="w-full sm:w-auto px-12 py-5 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300 shadow-2xl shadow-blue-500/20 hover:-translate-y-1" data-ps="src/pages/industries/textiles.astro:y6o4u0">
            Request Early Access
          </button>
          <a href="/platform/why-tieback/" class="group text-slate-900 font-bold flex items-center gap-3 transition-colors hover:text-blue-600" data-ps="src/pages/industries/textiles.astro:1gb7hp">
            Why TieBack <svg class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
